Sorting algorithms in C++ and ASM

This rep contains implementation of few popular sorting algorithms 
written in C++ and assembler languages (only three of them for the moment). 
Just a few brief details are given in the code. 

Tested with GNU gcc version 13.3

Building on Linux:
 cd <cloned_directory>
 cmake . && cmake --build .

In case other than standard compiler is needed, the one can be
specified using the environment variable CXX before the 
running cmake:

 export CXX=/usr/bin/g++-13
 cmake . && cmake --build .

Please let me know if you have any questions.

Ruslan Satlykov <pzxmtx@yandex.ru>
